# Smoke-First, Small Scope

- Default new page coverage to a load/shell smoke (`goto` + key UI visible) before deep flows.
- One page or feature per change set. Do not expand into unrelated modules “while here.”
- Prefer extending an existing smoke file/page object when the page already has a sibling pattern (e.g. Live Data).
- Deeper happy paths come later in a separate PR once the smoke is green.
- No drive-by refactors, docs, or config churn unrelated to the current page/feature.
